This project is written in C++ and it is built on previous C project.

In preious project, the monster move is not fully implemented
so that in this project monsters have only one movement parttern.
Monster movement will be fully implemented in future project.

Teleport into immutable rock is impossible, because the teleport
pointer can not even move to the out most layer of the dungeon.

Press key f to toggle the fog of war on and off.